data.description: Welcome into this well designed townhome with a sophisticated neutral palette. Natural light floods the dining/breakfast area that leads to the galley kitchen, where creating Holiday dishes will be a delight! The generously sized living room is a great space for entertaining with french door access to the deck for grilling. A half bath rounds out the main level. Upstairs, find 3 light and bright bedrooms. The master has a walk-in closet and plenty of room for your creature comforts. A full bath is easily accessible to all bedrooms. The laundry room is located in the basement, along with an ample size garage. Enjoy new a/c, new garage door, a newer hot water heater, new sidewalk and new screens on all windows, including a slider. Enjoy the community pool, tennis & basketball court, playgrounds and more. Convenient to shopping, entertainment, and major highways. Don't miss this opportunity, make your appointment today!
